docteur jekyll et les femmes , also known as blood of dr. jekyll , is a 1981 french – west german horror film directed by walerian borowczyk .   the film is a variation on robert louis stevenson 's story strange case of dr jekyll and mr hyde and stars udo kier , marina pierro , patrick magee , howard vernon and gérard zalcberg .   the film was released in france in 1981 and won the award for " best feature film director " at the 1981 sitges film festival for borowczyk .